# ==================================================================
# EMAIL VERIFICATION SERVICE CONFIGURATION
# ==================================================================
# Add ONE of these API keys to enable email verification
# The system will automatically use the first available provider
# ==================================================================

# Hunter.io Email Verification (Recommended for B2B)
# Free tier: 50 verifications/month
# Paid: $49/month for 500 verifications
# Sign up: https://hunter.io/users/sign_up
# HUNTER_API_KEY=your_hunter_api_key_here

# ZeroBounce Email Verification (Most Accurate)
# Free tier: 100 credits
# Paid: $16/month for 2,000 validations
# Sign up: https://www.zerobounce.net/members/register/
# ZEROBOUNCE_API_KEY=your_zerobounce_api_key_here

# AbstractAPI Email Validation (Budget-friendly)
# Free tier: 250 requests/month
# Paid: $9/month for 10,000 requests
# Sign up: https://app.abstractapi.com/users/signup
# ABSTRACTAPI_KEY=your_abstractapi_key_here

# ==================================================================
# If NO API key is provided, the system will use Basic verification
# Basic verification only checks:
# - Email syntax (RFC 5322)
# - Common disposable domains
# ==================================================================
